The evidence with the title 'North Dakota - Wikipedia ' says North Dakota is a U.S. state in the midwestern and northern regions of the United States . It is the nineteenth largest in area, the fourth smallest by population, and the fourth most sparsely populated of the 50 states . North Dakota was admitted to the Union on november 2 , 1889, along with its  ... The chief crop , wheat, is grown in nearly every county . 
